race.comment: POWERHOUSE (2) resumed off Group company and went close here at Beaumont. Switched to this course after and was beaten a whisker stepping up to this trip. Fitter again and was a comfortable third-up winner here previously. Races forward and he can go one better. CELLARMASTER (1) rates a threat. Got a mile back in a rich Magic Millions feature a month ago following a convincing Maiden win as favourite at Randwick. The in-form Latham is off the above to ride and the betting should guide to his readiness. AFLOAT (6) ran a better race second-up, beaten 2L over 1400m at this track after being in contention on the turn. Has his share of ability and should get every chance from the inside. Hard to beat in this suitable race. NGUNNAWAL (5) resumed over 1625m at Wyong beaten only 1.5 lengths. Fitter and has more to give. Sure to run well. ISLA NEGRA (9) peaks and should be ready to show more.
